@startuml

title WallRunner v3.0 — 房间生命周期状态图

[*] --> Empty : 房主创建房间
Empty --> Waiting : 等待访客加入
Waiting --> Playing : 房主点击开始
Waiting --> Waiting : 访客加入
Waiting --> Dissolved : 房主离开
Playing --> Playing : 玩家加入/离开
Playing --> GameOver : 所有玩家死亡
GameOver --> Waiting : 房主重新开始
GameOver --> Dissolved : 房主离开
Dissolved --> [*] : 房间销毁

state Waiting {
    [*] --> HostOnly
    HostOnly --> HasGuests : 访客加入
    HasGuests --> HostOnly : 访客离开
}

state Playing {
    [*] --> Active
    Active --> PlayerDisconnected : 玩家掉线
    PlayerDisconnected --> Active : 玩家重连
    Active --> AllDead : 所有玩家死亡
    AllDead --> [*] : 进入GameOver
}

note right of Waiting
  房间号：6位UUID大写
  自动分配不重复颜色
end note

note right of Playing
  掉线玩家标记为disconnected
  保留数据便于重连
end note
@enduml
